热难耐</span></p><p begin="00:27.053" end="00:29.481" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:27.053" end="00:27.174">た</span><span begin="00:27.174" end="00:27.302">だ</span><span begin="00:27.302" end="00:27.554">風</span><span begin="00:27.554" end="00:27.768">が</span><span begin="00:27.768" end="00:27.903">吹</span><span begin="00:27.903" end="00:28.027">く</span><span begin="00:28.027" end="00:28.157">の</span><span begin="00:28.157" end="00:28.274">を</span><span begin="00:28.274" end="00:28.753">待</span><span begin="00:28.753" end="00:28.975">って</span><span begin="00:28.975" end="00:29.481">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只是静候着一缕清风</span></p><p begin="00:30.900" end="00:33.224" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:30.900" end="00:31.123">木</span><span begin="00:31.123" end="00:31.899">陰</span><span begin="00:31.899" end="00:32.195">に</span><span begin="00:32.195" end="00:32.828">座</span><span begin="00:32.828" end="00:33.224">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">坐在树荫下</span></p><p begin="00:34.768" end="00:36.911" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:34.768" end="00:35.440">何</span><span begin="00:35.440" end="00:35.566">か</span><span begin="00:35.566" end="00:36.172">頬</span><span begin="00:36.172" end="00:36.386">に</span><span begin="00:36.386" end="00:36.644">付</span><span begin="00:36.644" end="00:36.911">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有什么东西粘上了脸颊</span></p><p begin="00:38.573" end="00:43.204" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:38.573" end="00:38.838">見</span><span begin="00:38.838" end="00:39.304">上</span><span begin="00:39.304" end="00:39.554">げ</span><span begin="00:39.554" end="00:39.943">れ</span><span begin="00:39.943" end="00:40.204">ば</span><span begin="00:40.204" end="00:40.446">頭</span><span begin="00:40.446" end="00:41.202">上</span><span begin="00:41.202" end="00:41.499">に</span><span begin="00:41.499" end="00:41.708">咲</span><span begin="00:41.708" end="00:41.936">い</span><span begin="00:41.936" end="00:42.124">て</span><span begin="00:42.124" end="00:42.425">散</span><span begin="00:42.425" end="00:43.204">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">向上望去，头顶一片花开花落</span></p><p begin="00:45.758" end="00:49.644" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:45.758" end="00:46.018">は</span><span begin="00:46.018" end="00:46.266">ら</span><span begin="00:46.266" end="00:46.493">り、</span><span begin="00:46.493" end="00:46.994">僕</span><span begin="00:46.994" end="00:47.335">ら</span><span begin="00:47.335" end="00:47.531">も</span><span begin="00:47.531" end="00:47.725">う</span><span begin="00:47.949" end="00:48.428">息</span><span begin="00:48.428" end="00:48.632">も</span><span begin="00:48.632" end="00:49.169">忘</span><span begin="00:49.169" end="00:49.385">れ</span><span begin="00:49.385" end="00:49.644">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">飞花飘零，我们连呼吸也忘却</span></p><p begin="00:49.889" end="00:53.461" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:49.889" end="00:50.805">瞬</span><span begin="00:50.805" end="00:51.142">き</span><span begin="00:51.142" end="00:51.334">さ</span><span begin="00:51.334" end="00:51.491">え</span><span begin="00:51.491" end="00:52.019">億</span><span begin="00:52.019" end="00:53.461">劫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">甚至不愿眨眼</span></p><p begin="00:53.644" end="00:57.490" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:53.644" end="00:53.844">さ</span><span begin="00:53.844" end="00:54.159">ぁ、</span><span begin="00:54.159" end="00:54.381">今</span><span begin="00:54.381" end="00:54.633">日</span><span begin="00:54.633" end="00:54.904">さ</span><span begin="00:54.904" end="00:55.151">え</span><span begin="00:55.151" end="00:55.373">明</span><span begin="00:55.373" end="00:55.845">日</span><span begin="00:55.845" end="00:56.078">過</span><span begin="00:56.078" end="00:56.363">去</span><span begin="00:56.363" end="00:56.582">に</span><span begin="00:56.582" 