:09.514">だ</span><span begin="01:09.514" end="01:10.015">花</span><span begin="01:10.015" end="01:10.252">が</span><span begin="01:10.252" end="01:10.742">降</span><span begin="01:10.742" end="01:10.983">る</span><span begin="01:10.983" end="01:11.220">だ</span><span begin="01:11.220" end="01:12.197">け</span><span begin="01:12.888" end="01:13.138">晴</span><span begin="01:13.138" end="01:13.382">れ</span><span begin="01:13.382" end="01:13.714">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只是落花纷纷</span></p><p begin="01:13.857" end="01:16.756" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:13.857" end="01:14.580">今、</span><span begin="01:14.580" end="01:15.054">春</span><span begin="01:15.054" end="01:15.528">吹</span><span begin="01:15.528" end="01:16.756">雪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">此刻，阳光明媚，樱飞漫天</span></p><p begin="01:32.596" end="01:34.651" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:32.596" end="01:32.766">次</span><span begin="01:32.766" end="01:32.927">の</span><span begin="01:32.927" end="01:33.089">日</span><span begin="01:33.089" end="01:33.304">も</span><span begin="01:33.304" end="01:33.557">待</span><span begin="01:33.557" end="01:33.807">ち</span><span begin="01:33.807" end="01:34.041">合</span><span begin="01:34.041" end="01:34.262">わ</span><span begin="01:34.262" end="01:34.651">せ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">第二天也是碰头的日子</span></p><p begin="01:36.432" end="01:39.101" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:36.432" end="01:36.648">花</span><span begin="01:36.648" end="01:36.803">見</span><span begin="01:36.803" end="01:36.926">の</span><span begin="01:36.926" end="01:37.094">客</span><span begin="01:37.094" end="01:37.250">も</span><span begin="01:37.250" end="01:37.614">少</span><span begin="01:37.614" end="01:37.869">な</span><span begin="01:37.869" end="01:38.105">く</span><span begin="01:38.105" end="01:38.590">な</span><span begin="01:38.590" end="01:39.101">った</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xm